{
  "stem": "2804.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I did not know how to swim at the time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and I had very poor equilibrium.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Even going today on a ship or on the plane, I always take Dramamine or something.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the 10 days going over, maybe 8 out of the 10 days I was seasick.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not that I can remember, no.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I really don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I really don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we finally got into Le Havre.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they had the landing, the LSTs take us from the ship into Le Havre.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when we got into Le Havre, they had camps there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was funny.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Why, I don't know, but they were named after cigarettes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They had Camp Camel, Camp Chesterfield, Camp Lucky Strike at the time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And our-- our unit, our men stayed in Le Havre at these camps.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we nurses were put on a bus, rather on a two-ton truck we had.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we went 50 miles north of Le Havre to a small place called Reims or Neufchatel, that was a little city.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we got there about 9 o'clock at night.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it was a chateau.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was built and shaped in a U form.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was empty.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I understand that was used as a school for the children.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They had nuns that took care of them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But when we got there, it was empty.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Now, where they went, I do not know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But every-- about every 20 feet, when we got there, there was a potbelly stove.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And the pipe went up, and there was a pane of glass that was out, and out went the-- you know, if we lit them up, the smoke went out the window.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And if the wind blew the other way, the smoke came in.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
